column5: 28" Steamboat on crawler harness.

Hey, guys. I live in Olathe and work in Lee's Summit. Small world, huh? Mike Kansas, I think we've talked before. Made my fifth trip to Goose Bay Camp on Lac Seul this year. End of May. Numbers were down a little, but caught nice size. Walleyefisher, where do you like to fish in the area?
Walleyefisher, I live in Olathe. Dont do much fishing in Kansas. Where do you live in KC? Mike
I live in Lees Summit. Where do you fish then??? or do you just not fish locally? Email me if you want. Walleyefisher at yahoo.com

I go on four or five trips a year mostly to Canada. Last year my wife and I went Red Fishing at Venice La. and had a ball. I dont own a boat and feel I cant really justify one. It seems such a waste to haul a boat to Canada. There are times I have considered buying a boat to fish some of the local Walleye lakes but I always chicken out at the last. Mike Kansas
Why does the tag line ask for the largest walleye, and then people post smaller ones than some other person already posted.
29.5" - Six foot snell, yellow bead.
34.5 - 13pd3ozs Shrimp hotntot Big filliets.
Logcatcher, where and when was this caught, where were you staying?
We were at the Sioux Lookout, fish caught in 17fow, 105 back, varying between 2.0 and 2.5mph
a hair shy of 31 inches - 11 lbs. My 16 yr old son caught it on a chartruse jig and crawle. He released it to fight another day and having a replica made. I was very proud of him....
JR Derksen.....13"......Worm & Bobber on Snoopy Rod
29 1/2" on during the opener. Used a green jig and a minnow in 12' of water. My biggest was 31 1/2" two years ago in the same location, using a spinner and a minnow.
5/23 the first fish i caught this year at chamberlain was 29.25 in.
Mike Sarenskii....Kansas. didn't actually catch any himself but saw a guy in another boat catch some.
To IAwalleye. The 8 year old is catching bigger fish than you because he hasn't learned all of your bad habits.
Janet Saresky......Evergreen Lodge...6/28/04 ......31 1/2 " Walleye...Rapala Crankbait Perch
Brad Dunham-----28" Walleye------Williams Bay----Jig and Leech cant match Miss Janet and her Monster
may 16th at Honey point 29", Pink and white
Josh Kelly----7/1/04-----29"----jig/minnow------Granite Island
Where in Kansas are you? I live in KC and fish most of the area lakes and thought I might have seen you.
Lets find out who caught the biggest Walleye this year on Lac Seul. Rick Grunden, Pilot Grove Mo... 6/3/04....29 1/4"

My 8-year old daughter caught a 27.5" on a jig and a 27 on a spinner/bottom bouncer. Second year in a row the kids did better than the old man!...IA Walleye

Had some friends staying at Goose Bay a couple of weeks ago. Because of a tremendous wind, they were not able to get out on the lake one of the days. They caught about 40 walleyes vertical jigging off the dock, with the biggest being 28.5"!
